Anglo Platinum Worker Found Dead at Its Rustenburg Operation, Union Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-31T12:55:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/anglo-platinum-worker-found-dead-at-its-rustenburg-operation-union-says.html
A mineworker who went missing
yesterday at Anglo American Platinum Ltd.’s Rustenburg operation
has been found dead, according to the National Union of
Mineworkers.  “The cause of death is not yet known,” the labor union
said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  